  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this the study is to the assess whether the graft and patient survival, rejection
      rates and renal graft function after the first year will not differ between both study arms.
      The investigators will also the evaluate the reduction in the incidence of cytomegalovirus
      the and improvement of renal function of the everolimus after 1 year.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
